title: Man, 20, dies after car leaves A59 and crashes
title_page: Man, 20, dies after car leaves A59 and crashes - BBC News
maintext:
A 20-year-old man has died after the car he was driving left the road and crashed into an embankment.
Police were called to reports the Skoda Octavia had left the A59, Harrogate to York road, between Moor Monkton and Green Hammerton at about 22:30 GMT on Monday.
The driver, who has yet to be named, was pronounced dead at the scene.
His passenger, a 19-year-old woman, remains in a serious condition in hospital, a North Yorkshire Police spokesperson said.
